{"tid":1990133,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"大根放話告網友 吳宗憲酸「等你變巨根」","createTime":"2020-04-26T12:50:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T14:50:04.000Z","uid":304179,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a6dd7135eb3823d72a66734f54534b6348aecd57","tid":1990133,"uid":304179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T12:50:37.000Z","msg":"小豬分手周揚青，周揚青指小豬和好友們對約出來的女生很不尊重，甚至還進行「多人運動」，這把火也燒到小豬好兄弟大根，大根的臉書遭網友攻陷，讓大根忍不住發怒提告，不過後來他又悄悄刪除發文，吳宗憲(憲哥)今錄影被問到此事，直言「<strong>大根算了啦！等你變大咖一點，變成『巨根』的時候，等人家告你，你還這麼小咖，刪文就對了嘛！</strong>」<br />\n<br />\n憲哥還現場模擬大根上法庭的情境，酸法官可能連他是藝人都不知道，「<strong>去到庭上說有人毀損名譽，法官可能還會問說，你是大根啊，大先生請問你從事什麼行業？</strong>」勸大根有時候還是要有點雅量。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://stars.udn.com/star/story/10091/4520140\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstars.udn.com%2Fstar%2Fstory%2F10091%2F4520140&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4JE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=5a3d3c08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://stars.udn.com/star/story/10091/4520140</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑撚死"},{"pid":"4d828cbde56b06134e905aafaa620b280e307d2e","tid":1990133,"uid":42246,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T12:52:42.000Z","msg":"吳宗憲根本就係台版叻哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17f9f76f7b365da7505917017011d7b1fc02df73","tid":1990133,"uid":304179,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4d828cbde56b06134e905aafaa620b280e307d2e","tid":1990133,"uid":42246,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T12:52:42.000Z","msg":"吳宗憲根本就係台版叻哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T12:56:35.000Z","msg":"勁口賤<img src=\"/a